snippet.title: Pinball Masters | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Channel your inner pinball wizard! Flip and tilt your way through themed tables featuring characters like Godzilla and Kong in this classic arcade game.

Play Pinball Masters on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81665065

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 247 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
